{{infobox book |name = Micronations: The Lonely Planet Guide to Home-Made Nations |image = Micro cover.jpg |author = J. Ryan,<ref name="Google"/> G. Dunford, and S. Sellars<ref name="Amazon"/> |pages = 156<ref name="Google">{{cite book |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=5ZRrwrlIPSYC&printsec=frontcover&source=gbs_atb#v=onepage&q&f=false |title=Micronations - John Ryan |website=Google Books |publisher=Lonely Planet Publications Party Ltd |date=September 2006 |accessdate=26 January 2014 |isbn13=978-1741047301}}</ref> |publisher = Lonely Planet |published = 2006<ref name="Google"/> |isbn = 978-1741047301 |isbn_note=<ref name="Amazon">{{cite book |url=https://www.amazon.com/Micronations-Lonely-Planet-Home-Made-Nations/dp/1741047307 |title=Micronations: The Lonely Planet Guide to Home-Made Nations |first=John |last=Ryan |first2=George |last2=Dunford |first3=Simon |last3=Sellars |publisher=Lonely Planet Publications Party Ltd |date=September 2006 |website=Amazon.com |accessdate=26 January 2014 |isbn13=978-1741047301}}</ref> }}
'''''Micronations: The Lonely Planet Guide to Home-Made Nations''''' is a [[gazetteer]] published by [[Lonely Planet]]. It has also been published under the name '''''Micronations: The Lonely Planet Guide to Self-Proclaimed Nations'''''. It was written by John Ryan, George Dunford and Simon Sellars.
==Micronations featured== The book's profile of [[micronations]] offers information on their [[Flags of micronations|flag]]s, [[micronational heads of state|leaders]], [[Micronational currency systems|currencies]], date of foundation, [[map]]s and other facts. [[Sidebar (publishing)|Sidebar]]s throughout the book provide overviews of such topics as [[micronational currency systems|coins]] and [[Cinderella stamp|stamps]] and a profile of [[Emperor Norton]].
Micronations featured in the book include: *[[Principality of Sealand|Sealand]] *[[Freetown Christiania]] *[[Principality of Hutt River]] *[[Kingdom of Lovely|Lovely]] *[[Whangamomona]] *[[Sovereign Military Order of Malta]] *[[Kingdom of Elleore|Elleore]] *[[Akhzivland]] *Northern Forest Archipelago *[[Principality of Seborga|Seborga]] *[[Principality of Freedonia|Freedonia]] *[[Republic of Molossia|Molossia]] *Copeman Empire *[[Empire of Atlantium|Atlantium]] *[[North Dumpling Island]] *[[Kugelmugel]] *[[Grand Duchy of the Lagoan Isles|Lagoan Isles]] *[[Kingdom of Vikesland|Vikesland]] *[[Romkerhall]] *Kemetia *[[Aerican Empire|Aerica]] *Trumania *Westarctica *Eastport *[[Republic of Saugeais|Saugeais]] *SoS (State of Sabotage) *[[Conch Republic]] *[[Ladonia (micronation)|Ladonia]] *[[Dominion of British West Florida|British West Florida]] *Elsanor *[[Snake Hill]]
